## Examples

**Insert**
```ts
// Using object helper for cleaner syntax
const userData = {
  name: "Alice",
  email: "alice@example.com",
};

const [newUser] = await sql`
  INSERT INTO users ${sql(userData)}
  RETURNING *
`;
